{
  "info": {
    "name": "SmartRent - SePay Payment Gateway",
    "description": "End-to-end test collection for the SePay Payment Gateway (Cổng thanh toán) integration.\n\n## Flow\n1. **Auth → Login** — gets a Bearer token (saved to `accessToken`).\n2. **Initiate** a payment (membership purchase/upgrade, push, post, VIP, repost) with `\"paymentProvider\": \"SEPAY\"`. The response's `transactionRef` and `amount` are auto-saved. `providerData.checkoutUrl` + `providerData.fields` are the signed checkout form the frontend POSTs to SePay.\n3. The user pays on SePay's hosted checkout. SePay then confirms via the **IPN** (`POST /v1/payments/webhook/sepay`, `X-Secret-Key` header). Either:\n   - complete a real test payment on the sandbox checkout, OR\n   - **Simulate the IPN** with *SePay IPN (simulate)* — sends `X-Secret-Key: {{sepaySecretKey}}` and a nested ORDER_PAID payload whose `order.order_invoice_number` = the saved `transactionRef`.\n4. **Poll** `GET /transactions/{txnRef}` until `status` = `COMPLETED`.\n\n## Setup\nSet collection variables: `baseUrl`, `email`, `password`, and `sepaySecretKey` (must equal the backend's `SEPAY_SECRET_KEY`).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "email", "value": "john.doe@example.com", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "password", "value": "SecurePass123!", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "accessToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "sepaySecretKey", "value": "YOUR_SEPAY_PG_SECRET_KEY", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "transactionRef", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "amount", "value": "1400000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "membershipId", "value": "2", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "targetMembershipId", "value": "2", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "listingId", "value": "123", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (get token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "if (res.data && res.data.accessToken) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', res.data.accessToken);",
                  "    console.log('accessToken saved');",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('Got access token', () => pm.expect(res.data.accessToken).to.be.a('string'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth"]
            },
            "description": "Authenticate and store the access token in {{accessToken}} for the rest of the collection."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Initiate (SEPAY)",
      "description": "Each initiate endpoint returns a PaymentResponse. The test script saves transactionRef and amount so the IPN + polling requests work without manual copy-paste. providerData.checkoutUrl + providerData.fields are the signed checkout form to POST to SePay.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Membership - Initiate Purchase",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const d = res.data || {};",
                  "if (d.transactionRef) pm.collectionVariables.set('transactionRef', d.transactionRef);",
                  "if (d.amount) pm.collectionVariables.set('amount', String(d.amount));",
                  "pm.test('provider is SEPAY', () => pm.expect(d.provider).to.eql('SEPAY'));",
                  "pm.test('has transactionRef', () => pm.expect(d.transactionRef).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "pm.test('has signed checkout fields', () => pm.expect(d.providerData.fields.signature).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "console.log('transactionRef:', d.transactionRef, '| checkoutUrl:', d.providerData && d.providerData.checkoutUrl, '| amount:', d.amount);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"membershipId\": {{membershipId}},\n  \"paymentProvider\": \"SEPAY\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/memberships/initiate-purchase",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "memberships", "initiate-purchase"]
            },
            "description": "POST providerData.fields (in order) to providerData.checkoutUrl to send the user to SePay's hosted checkout."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Membership - Initiate Upgrade",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const d = res.data || {};",
                  "if (d.transactionRef) pm.collectionVariables.set('transactionRef', d.transactionRef);",
                  "if (d.finalAmount != null) pm.collectionVariables.set('amount', String(d.finalAmount));",
                  "console.log('status:', d.status, '| paymentUrl:', d.paymentUrl, '| finalAmount:', d.finalAmount);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"targetMembershipId\": {{targetMembershipId}},\n  \"paymentProvider\": \"SEPAY\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/memberships/initiate-upgrade",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "memberships", "initiate-upgrade"]
            },
            "description": "If the discount covers the full price the response status is COMPLETED with no checkout (no IPN needed)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Push - Pay per push",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const d = res.data || {};",
                  "const payment = d.payment || d;",
                  "if (payment.transactionRef) pm.collectionVariables.set('transactionRef', payment.transactionRef);",
                  "if (payment.amount) pm.collectionVariables.set('amount', String(payment.amount));",
                  "console.log('push response:', JSON.stringify(d));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"listingId\": {{listingId}},\n  \"useMembershipQuota\": false,\n  \"paymentProvider\": \"SEPAY\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/pushes/push",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "pushes", "push"]
            },
            "description": "Pay-per-post, VIP listing and repost follow the same pattern — send paymentProvider=SEPAY when not using membership quota."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "SePay IPN (simulate)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const res = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.test('Status 200 (SePay ack)', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
              "pm.test('success = true', () => pm.expect(res.success).to.eql(true));",
              "console.log('IPN acked. Now poll GET /transactions/{{transactionRef}} for COMPLETED.');"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
          { "key": "X-Secret-Key", "value": "{{sepaySecretKey}}", "description": "SePay sends our Secret Key here. Backend returns 401 if it doesn't match SEPAY_SECRET_KEY." }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"timestamp\": 1759134682,\n  \"notification_type\": \"ORDER_PAID\",\n  \"order\": {\n    \"order_invoice_number\": \"{{transactionRef}}\",\n    \"order_status\": \"CAPTURED\",\n    \"order_amount\": \"{{amount}}.00\"\n  },\n  \"transaction\": {\n    \"transaction_id\": \"68ba94ac80123\",\n    \"transaction_status\": \"APPROVED\",\n    \"transaction_amount\": \"{{amount}}\",\n    \"payment_method\": \"BANK_TRANSFER\"\n  }\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/webhook/sepay",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["v1", "payments", "webhook", "sepay"]
        },
        "description": "Simulates the SePay Payment Gateway IPN. The backend matches `order.order_invoice_number` to the pending transaction, requires notification_type=ORDER_PAID + transaction_status=APPROVED and transaction_amount >= order amount, marks it COMPLETED and triggers business logic.\n\nRun an *Initiate* request first so {{transactionRef}} and {{amount}} are populated."
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "SePay IPN - Bad secret key (expect 401)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status 401', () => pm.response.to.have.status(401));",
              "const res = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.test('success = false', () => pm.expect(res.success).to.eql(false));"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
          { "key": "X-Secret-Key", "value": "wrong-key-123" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"notification_type\": \"ORDER_PAID\",\n  \"order\": { \"order_invoice_number\": \"{{transactionRef}}\", \"order_status\": \"CAPTURED\", \"order_amount\": \"{{amount}}.00\" },\n  \"transaction\": { \"transaction_status\": \"APPROVED\", \"transaction_amount\": \"{{amount}}\" }\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/webhook/sepay",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["v1", "payments", "webhook", "sepay"]
        },
        "description": "Negative test: a wrong/missing X-Secret-Key header must be rejected with HTTP 401."
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Query / Poll",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Query Transaction (poll until COMPLETED)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const status = res.data && res.data.status;",
                  "console.log('Transaction status:', status);",
                  "pm.test('status present', () => pm.expect(status).to.be.oneOf(['PENDING','COMPLETED','FAILED','CANCELLED','REFUNDED']));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [ { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" } ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/transactions/{{transactionRef}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "payments", "transactions", "{{transactionRef}}"]
            },
            "description": "Frontend polls this every ~3s. After the IPN fires, status flips to COMPLETED."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Check Transaction Exists",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/exists/{{transactionRef}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "payments", "exists", "{{transactionRef}}"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Available Providers",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/providers",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "payments", "providers"]
            },
            "description": "Should return [\"SEPAY\"]."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Payment History",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [ { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" } ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/history?userId={{userId}}&page=1&size=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "payments", "history"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "userId", "value": "{{userId}}" },
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "size", "value": "20" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Payment History by Status",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [ { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" } ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/history/status/COMPLETED?userId={{userId}}&page=1&size=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "payments", "history", "status", "COMPLETED"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "userId", "value": "{{userId}}" },
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "size", "value": "20" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "status path segment: PENDING | COMPLETED | FAILED | CANCELLED | REFUNDED"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Manage",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Cancel Payment",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" } ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/cancel/{{transactionRef}}?reason=User%20closed",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "payments", "cancel", "{{transactionRef}}"],
              "query": [ { "key": "reason", "value": "User%20closed" } ]
            },
            "description": "Cancels a PENDING transaction (best-effort SePay order/cancel + local CANCELLED)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refund / Void Payment",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" } ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/refund/{{transactionRef}}?amount={{amount}}&reason=Customer%20request",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "payments", "refund", "{{transactionRef}}"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "amount", "value": "{{amount}}" },
                { "key": "reason", "value": "Customer%20request" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Voids a card transaction via SePay order/voidTransaction. Bank transfers are not auto-refundable."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
